snippet.title: Hey Dukh Bhanjan Maruti Nandan | Sun Lo Meri Pukar | Hanuman Bhajan | Shree Dhun
snippet.description:
seek refuge in the feet of Lord Hanuman, the remover of all sorrows, with the soulful bhajan "Hey Dukh Bhanjan Maruti Nandan," presented by Shree Dhun.

(à¤¹à¥‡ à¤¦à¥à¤– à¤­à¤‚à¤œà¤¨ à¤®à¤¾à¤°à¥à¤¤à¤¿ à¤¨à¤‚à¤¦à¤¨ - à¤¸à¥à¤¨ à¤²à¥‹ à¤®à¥‡à¤°à¥€ à¤ªà¥à¤•à¤¾à¤°)

This bhajan is a heartfelt prayer to Bajrangbali (Maruti Nandan). The devotee calls out to Him as "Dukh Bhanjan" (The Destroyer of Grief), asking for protection, strength, and the removal of all pain. Listening to this song brings immense relief to a troubled heart.

Lyrics Highlight: Hey Dukh Bhanjan Maruti Nandan, Sun Lo Meri Pukar... Pavan Sut Vinti Barambar...
